{"body":"Where the period in respect of which a renter is liable to make a relevant payment is not a month, an amount is to be calculated as the monthly equivalent, so for example weekly payments are multiplied by 52 and divided by 12.","citation_label":"UKSI 2013/376 Sch. 4 para. 7","citation_path":"uk/regulation/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/7","document_class":"regulation","expression_date":"2026-06-06","heading":"Relevant payments calculated monthly","id":"68f3dc7a-6a44-5f6e-aaa6-82dd52f51b1e","jurisdiction":"uk","kind":"regulation","language":"en","legal_identifier":"Universal Credit Regulations 2013 Sch. 4 para. 7","level":1,"metadata":{"retrieved_at":"2026-06-06T12:50:00Z"},"ordinal":7,"parent_citation_path":"uk/regulation/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4","source_as_of":"2026-06-06","source_document_id":"uksi/2013/376","source_format":"legislation.gov.uk-html","source_id":"https://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/7","source_url":"https://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/7","version":"2026-06-06-uk-universal-credit-schedule4-paragraph7"}
